{{Potd page|1= Ing pangalarawan kang [[:en:Allan Quartermain|Allan Quartermain]], metung a tauan kareng novela nang [[:en:H. Rider Haggard|H. Rider Haggard]], a mangasu kareng mangaragul a animal,  ketang linimbag ning ''[[:en:Harper's Magazine|Harper's Magazine]]'' a ''Maiwa's Revenge'' (1888). I Allan Quartermain ing bida king makabang serie da reng novela, nung nu ing ''[[:en:King Solomon's Mines|King Solomon's Mines]]'' ing pekasikat. Ginulis neng Thure de Thulstrup.|2=pam|3=2009|4=07|5=31}}
